name: Prototyping in Figma (Finnish)
description:
Learn the basics of Figma prototyping in Finnish using this translated version of the default file that comes with a new account.


Opi Figman prototyyppauksen perusteet virallisella Figma -tiedostolla jonka käänsimme suomeksi.


Katso myös Figman perusteet tiedoston: https://www.figma.com/community/file/958644165146205750/Figma-Basics-(Finnish)
